1. *Pesma* je jedan od najlepših načina da se izrazi čovekova duša. (The song is one of the most beautiful ways to express a man's soul.) 

2. *Pesme* se pevaju u mnogim različitim stilovima. (Songs are sung in many different styles.) 

3. Ova *pesma* je umetničko delo. (This song is an artwork.) 

4. On je napisao tu *pesmu* pre nekoliko dana. (He wrote that song a few days ago.) 

5. *Pesmu* smo svi zajedno pevali. (We all sang the song together.) 

6. Oni su se smejali dok su čitali *pesmu*. (They laughed while reading the song.)